QuestData.Title: The Final Reagent
QuestData.Description:
I have gathered most of the remaining reagents on your master's list. All that remains is the special shipment he requested from Oribos.
The brokers have yet to deliver the shipment. When it arrives, your master will have all he needs to complete his ritual.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Bundle of Reagents to Balmedar in the House of Rituals.
QuestData.RewardText:
Let me hold onto these for now.
I will need you to get your hands on that shipment!
